/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢而家完全係以一個大陸官員嘅嘴臉對著你班蟻民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c98b389ebbd2c52988d95f17c4ebac0a2f0521","tid":160971,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:32:23.000Z","msg":"記者好波"},{"pid":"20d319dd7668c8d557746a1139aa3d29348edaaf","tid":160971,"uid":65381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:34:48.000Z","msg":"依啲唔係叫論壇，唔係雙向<br />\n林鄭之前仲簽署承諾保衛香港新聞自由<br />\n未做到巳經係咁<br />\n真係好擔心佢做到會點<br />\n成日we connect, we listen <br />\n得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61d634556c098c250550574071dc9407d9b040c","tid":160971,"uid":7937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大會無安排就屈林鄭拒絕採訪<br />\n<br />\n唔洗問一定又係毒果出既文<br />\n<br />\n等睇港豬齊齊中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你就係港豬啦 做五毛狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a6ee577e78fcb25e0eb0f5a3cd79e758f62a30","tid":160971,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:44:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d613945affe55329c620121003d845cc11fb1d1e","tid":160971,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:46:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}